description: [``botocore``] Add support for computer use tools
[``botocore``] Add support for computer use tools
[``botocore``] Add support for contact transfers in external voice systems.
[``botocore``] Adds defaultFontSize and defaultLineHeight as options in the EbuTtDDestinationSettings within the caption descriptions for an output stream.

[``botocore``] PrivateCA Connector for Active Directory now supports dual stack endpoints. This release adds the IpAddressType option to the VpcInformation on a Connector which determines whether the endpoint supports IPv4 only or IPv4 and IPv6 traffic.
[``botocore``] This release adds new StandardsControlsUpdatable field to the StandardsSubscription resource
[``botocore``] This release updates the default value of pprof-disabled from false to true.
